{"tid":2051485,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"全美示威潮後拜登選舉捐款大增","createTime":"2020-06-04T22:07:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T00:02:09.000Z","uid":28765,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ccb3f30a0ba81eda734ce8767f813823dc875bc6","tid":2051485,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T22:07:45.000Z","msg":"（中央社華盛頓4日綜合外電報導）由於明尼蘇達州值勤警察，以膝蓋壓制非裔男子佛洛伊德頸部致死掀起的抗議潮席捲全美，多個頂尖募款者聲稱，民主黨總統參選人拜登與盟友近日獲得的捐款暴增。<br />\n<br />\n拜登（Joe Biden）陣營的募款者說，佛洛依德（George Floyd）枉死引發全美抗議潮，總統川普因應之道，像是1日警方驅離位於華府公園的和平示威者，讓他能夠在教堂前供媒體拍攝，催出許多新捐款者，包括部分共和黨人也掏出支票簿。<br />\n<br />\n這位募款者把捐款湧入稱之為「熱切程度與奉獻規模的巨變」，不過他不願拿最近獲得的捐款總數與先前數額相比較，因拜登與民主黨全國委員會（Democratic National Committee）最近敲定的安排，允許更高額度捐款。<br />\n<br />\n美國前副總統拜登1日以電郵告訴支持者，在5月底的6天內，他的陣營線上募款，達到可觀的600萬美元（約新台幣1億7900萬元）目標。拜登將在11月3日的大選與現任共和黨籍總統川普對決。<br />\n<br />\n川普向來抨擊在抗爭期間行搶的那些人是「暴徒」，而他的陣營本週募款時重申，致力維護「法律與秩序」。<br />\n<br />\n拜登和民主黨4月間申報募得6050萬美元，略低於川普與其他委員會募到的6170萬美元。（譯者：曹宇帆/核稿：劉學源）1090604<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202006050002.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F202006050002.aspx&d=OUx24mKaoEPTVTG9WcU5EslSugA1I0CCabXjLbCjl00%3D&h=5feaf520\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202006050002.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/reuters/2020/06/04/us/politics/04reuters-minneapolis-police-democrats.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2Freuters%2F2020%2F06%2F04%2Fus%2Fpolitics%2F04reuters-minneapolis-police-democrats.html&d=OUx24mKaoEPTVTG9WcU5EslSugA1I0CCabXjLbCjl00%3D&h=5b606789\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nytimes.com/reuters/2020/06/04/us/politics/04reuters-minneapolis-police-democrats.html</a>"},{"pid":"67dbfe510fe8eaaebd6c0e601b5d535a1ff098dc","tid":2051485,"uid":176282,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T22:19:20.000Z","msg":"twitter一面倒屌侵<br />\n<br />\n但捐款多過中共登係咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8f447c2c8c00ec28d68584a78f32894263444ee","tid":2051485,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T22:21:06.000Z","msg":"咁樣侵應該好撚心急好想打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a638f75e7e4a53f5ef44eef17af8844a3743ea81","tid":2051485,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T23:04:52.000Z","msg":"不要再說了.jpg <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdfd08d63132ed0b6c0f03e22b3b789beefbd08d","tid":2051485,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T23:08:00.000Z","msg":"trump=777<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38576e9ca9e54b10f11ef6ea5d5647e84895e0d4","tid":2051485,"uid":335434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T00:02:09.000Z","msg":"傳說中嘅「人血漢堡」?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}